## Action Returns (Window Actions)

### Standard Pattern

```python
def action_view_intakes(self):
    """Navigate to intakes for this partner."""
    self.ensure_one()
    return {
        "type": "ir.actions.act_window",
        "name": f"Intakes — {self.name}",
        "res_model": "plasticos.intake",
        "view_mode": "list,form",
        "domain": [("partner_id", "=", self.id)],
        "context": {"default_partner_id": self.id},
    }
```

### Single Record Form

```python
def action_view_profile(self):
    self.ensure_one()
    return {
        "type": "ir.actions.act_window",
        "name": "Material Profile",
        "res_model": "plasticos.material.profile",
        "res_id": self.material_profile_id.id,
        "view_mode": "form",
        "target": "current",
    }
```

### Notification (No Window)

```python
def action_feature_disabled(self):
    return {
        "type": "ir.actions.client",
        "tag": "display_notification",
        "params": {
            "title": "Feature Disabled",
            "message": "This feature is handled externally.",
            "type": "warning",
        },
    }
```

