## XML Data Files

### Use `noupdate="1"` for Reference Data

```xml
<odoo noupdate="1">
    <record id="stage_active_supplier" model="crm.stage">
        <field name="name">Active Supplier</field>
        <field name="sequence">50</field>
    </record>
</odoo>
```

### External IDs for Lookups

```python
# ✅ CORRECT — Safe external ID lookup
stage = self.env.ref("plasticos_crm_bridge.stage_active_supplier", raise_if_not_found=False)
if stage:
    self.stage_id = stage
```

